		<title>Mayo Clinic scientists create tool to predict Alzheimer’s risk years before symptoms begin</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-scientists-create-tool-to-predict-alzheimers-risk-years-before-symptoms-begin/
		
		<dc:creator><!--[CDATA[Alison Satake]]--></dc:creator>
